Welcome to Tarirari Oasis! It may be scorching hot
outside, but here you can enjoy a resort-like
atmosphere! It may be scorching hot outside, but
here you can enjoy a resort-like atmosphere!

Have you ever gotten your hands on a promotional
flyer? You might be able to meet skilled
blacksmiths and merchants selling items that you
wouldn't normally find for sale!

This is a place where you can exchange \C[2]rare
metals\C[0] for treasures like gemstones and more!

I think I can occasionally get my hands on them,
but they're quite valuable. I collect them and
when I have a substantial amount, I sell them to
the blacksmith.

If you have any desired gemstones, I would love to
exchange them for rare metals and Lo. There are
also valuable gemstones available.

It's scorching outside, but here it feels like a
resort!

Have you ever gotten your hands on a promotional
flyer? You might be able to meet skilled
blacksmiths and merchants selling items that you
wouldn't normally find for sale!

Welcome back, it's you, Konoha, the one rumored to
be strong.

Has news about me spread even to a place like
this?

Of course! Even in remote places, information
spreads quickly! Well, that aside...

Have you fought against the enemies from the
desert? I think there are giant beings called
Titans.

Oh, right. The Titans you usually encounter in the
Big Salt Desert aren't really that strong, you
know.

There's a huge monster-class Titan rampaging
through the desert and causing trouble...

Even though they're already big, they're even
bigger?

Yeah, that's right. Their bodies aside, down there
is also pretty intense, so magical girls hate it
because their sexual desire is off the charts.

That's why customers don't come to this oasis as
much anymore. I'm in trouble.

So, you want me to defeat that monster-class
Titan...

I wonder... If you're as strong as you are, I
think you can do it.
Sure, I'll make it happen somehow
I'm a little busy right now

Either way, someone has to defeat it, right?
Alright, I'll give it a try.

Phew, I'm glad! I'll be saved~! Since that Titan
probably has a lot of stamina and all, be careful,
okay?
Hmm... I'm a bit busy at the moment.

This is a place where you can exchange \C[2] rare
metals \C[0] for treasures like gemstones.

I think I can get them occasionally, but they're
quite valuable. I collect them and when I have a
large quantity, I sell them to a blacksmith.

If you have any desired gemstones, please exchange
them with \C[2] rare metals \C[0] and Lo. There
are also valuable gemstones available.

Good job. If it happens again, we'll have to rely
on Konoha.
